        rating: 5,
        quote: "I recently purchased my second home with the help of Keyur (KB), and I could not be happier with the experience. From start to finish, everything was smooth, stress-free, and efficient. His expertise in loan options, rates, and paperwork made a huge difference. If you are looking for a knowledgeable and trustworthy mortgage broker, I highly recommend Keyur Bandhara.",
    },
    {
