        meta: "8 reviews | 3 photos",
        date: "2 May 2024",
        rating: 5,
        quote: "KB was recommended by a close friend and he has been extremely helpful. He showed dedication and commitment that enabled us to secure our goals. We have recommended him to our whole family and are very thankful for his support.",
    },
    {
        name: "Sumit Sharma",
